{"h28a6783cg4941g4c97g985bg2d0eca38474b": ["Leave me alone!", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "0d05643d-8f5e-ba9c-5b40-0551c5d02031"], "hab767e66gc7cag44b0g8309g95eaa1921ce7": ["The evil thing's gone! Now, where was I...", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "de5657d4-6b5f-915c-31e2-bfa1fefb2d4b"], "h5cbf5216g4e26g4536ga690g823893d80f9b": ["The evil thing's in the chest.", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "a3b6598b-10d6-5e35-028b-26f375e97479"], "hc9c10b55gcab0g4ddfgba80g9d4f9103a4cb": ["Stay back, or else!", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "2bc53151-9212-d393-4b91-7d3bd18f2084"], "hbca56348g0729g4a61gb79cg85d778b524a4": ["What's wrong?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "000dbbfc-aff3-59f9-6912-18e448439477"], "h1652288cgad8bg4480gb1c8g0137e78b941e": ["Nothing's wrong! Just get back!", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "3a512ab9-2d1c-0e50-f1fe-e2ee8aa1c487"], "h2c6b493bg0c17g4685g83b8gc4677c24f60b": ["Ow! My tooth...", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "6a8d82e2-cf98-19e1-c181-987d3c6eb421"], "hb4f1dc9fg2263g4186g83feg93ecf7c6d2d9": ["Let me take a look.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "ca9ad31c-d4e3-9376-557c-bf4a7e3d1bdf"], "h807fe0dbg0f4ag45bcgbd29g7660b706a804": ["It's the front one. I chipped it on the evil thing.", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "4b09300e-0b2f-9b5f-0ac0-ed6ba1c1df98"], "hc1456078g1175g4dcag99f1gb4811eebd6a7": ["<i>Laugh at him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "a1f082ea-ffdb-6bd9-d190-856a57bc541b"], "hbe1ca31cgb0eag4a5fg8d1bga550c13cbc55": ["It's not funny!", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "386ee1b7-b931-931a-7cbf-dc43795d82f7"], "h0990be91g23d9g40e4g8994g98eec3331574": ["I chipped it on the evil thing. It was horrible.", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "6c448c25-5943-9690-e024-672c404a7f5d"], "h05607c9dg177cg4283g827dg54ef43660a27": ["Were you trying to eat it?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "042f5ed1-e943-836f-57f5-97725046f744"], "h5a910c21g5e33g41adg9ff6gcc79568ae630": ["Maybe. I didn't think it would bite me back.", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "bf9b666b-4ddb-67ee-64c0-6561e2cf6adb"], "h1d4e0e17g35beg4dc3g9e85gb9eea39e44e1": ["Wait - you're big. You can get rid of the evil thing!", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "74528535-8b07-170c-25eb-a756b90110e5"], "hb7910279ga0eag4586gb30fg39e02bf07615": ["Follow me. But be ready for anything.", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "b3fc5ae2-507c-cd86-0025-8fe50d22a111"], "h26f3c2dag09d0g4e87g9dfdg3dae189afb1c": ["It looks fine to me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "b4e99785-062a-8bd4-b8d1-b1967169312b"], "h1e4ba0beg2712g4537ga81agb5b9d709231d": ["Does it? Oh, thank goodness. ", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "949923d6-0687-0455-7296-2ca5fdfe8f57"], "h7c4e6f91g54f6g4216g93bdg449b5457d057": ["What 'evil thing'?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "539cd7c6-74ae-6d84-7b43-06bfdf364b2b"], "h91a5aadfg5f44g40d7g98d0gd45dd04385ca": ["In the box. Follow me, I'll show you!", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "000ece9d-8720-5adb-b0d1-f3839ce0bff1"], "hfde270ddgc961g4ccfg89c2ge3ed45cf1b40": ["Sounds like your problem, not mine.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "65cc49c2-927e-a097-fec1-3c10eacf4edb"], "he0e535f1ga95fg4453g8bf2gf25b6fc9a414": ["You're no help!", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "5dee5ea4-4c56-82f7-bce6-912f05e85d3c"], "h57207ea5gf57ag4811gb9e7g35c58253d141": ["Good luck with that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "76e8d0fc-29aa-654f-025d-c06d4b93f8f3"], "hdf88e2d7g71eag45dag9ee8gf5b33b3baf8f": ["Or else <i>what</i>?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "17140042-3965-6d70-07a4-c1f17084b710"], "h5c4c164cgdba3g4cf4g8d89gf7e0a7cff57f": ["Or else, I'll - I'll bite you! ", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "d87c0148-15bd-707f-00c8-8b31947458ad"], "h6a15e825g9350g4606g988dg6682a9455aef": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "9ba3b0d8-6005-2e9a-c877-5f20f3ef4850"], "hc2fb4106gf723g4e09ga351gfb6acdec1d78": ["*The rat hisses at you, his eyes flashing distrustfully.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "18ff630c-241a-77a4-9a76-8b463428d202"], "hafb5c031g3aa4g4b17g8a60gf7481859b599": ["*Hiss!*", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "f8020cf4-607e-3045-54e8-ee0e0f74f230"], "h48034249g7d4eg406ega051g478eb8043acd": ["*The rat squeaks excitedly - the chest is free from danger once again.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "a848bc17-6f75-1bb0-2e6f-5b48626f8a5a"], "h156ed642g29cfg483bga2e0g6ebce2c5509d": ["*Eek!*", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "26ebf4c3-e2e9-e891-4fd4-d18ee1b301ae"], "h8a76bcbagdefcg4defgb60ag716b9db79a9d": ["*The rat chitters angrily - whatever broke his tooth is in this room.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "396e79d7-341a-536e-0b49-96838513928c"], "h9e2be064g839dg4670gb0bbg7fa0966c312a": ["*His dark eyes stare at you, eager for this danger to be banished.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "9f360121-08e9-0c85-456f-2ce90077d668"], "h3f7d30a9gfedfg48bag8b8bgb84f4df90524": ["*Eek! Eek!*", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "8ae2eb1d-3da5-8f90-3cd6-8757f18bd4a3"], "hab1c0377ga747g4b87gbf82ge616ceba0c4d": ["*Hiss!*", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "821c3ece-86bb-3559-1b97-33a0f4f3d2d6"], "h0ed4707ag6f61g4480g9eeegaca55d21df5e": ["<i>Hiss back.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "4a8f27ca-ab41-5e55-cffd-b43ffb5c353e"], "h159deab1g4594g4ae7g929cgdd7966b4de20": ["*Eek!*", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "2a69ac69-8179-26d9-9420-2ea6f70298c5"], "h7736a9cegaf10g4990gaaadg59ba38198a21": ["<i>Calm the creature.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "93a9550c-6d26-8ed4-5fbf-96767042016c"], "h58380373g7f36g4f11g8329g9341c8f5ba33": ["*The rat's eyes soften as he emits a pained squeak.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "57016179-ebfe-3659-93f8-712fd105e341"], "h290653f0gb318g434dgbc22gccd3b8ae1ad1": ["*You realise the source of his discomfort - one of his front teeth is chipped.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "d99553e6-0cb5-0563-4638-d3bf18cb7ae7"], "h506e9e48ga24bg4511g93b0gc67b3608dbd2": ["That's what gluttony will get you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "1b978f26-f08b-a570-ca05-2c9060680609"], "h3d15f537ga711g4651g92c2g61ab58fda2d1": ["*'Gluttony'? The rat squeaks in interest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "28aab9f8-efbe-5f6a-9d51-091184e2e761"], "h0be69e80gc9b6g4901gaff1gbf197fd536ab": ["*With an enthusiastic chitter, he urges you to follow.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "35e67fb3-ac69-f762-782d-fc35e76f2bc6"], "h781b99dagdb6dg4579g9341g6be4b7ae26ac": ["<i>Nod. He'll be fine.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "42ebce24-4b97-178a-9c17-5e56d8e508e3"], "h517c7bc3g7e41g4923gaef5gb4ba6bc6d49c": ["*The rat pauses, gauging whether his chipped tooth is, in fact, life threatening.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "291a04cb-f406-2664-b221-d2a5fc1ebfc3"], "hf10d8d7eg47b4g4911gb1a0g26edcefa194f": ["*Apparently satisfied, he beckons you with a squeak - follow.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "d05a37ad-40d3-10f0-9d8d-430d8376d007"], "h6a51c17fg7bf0g4a69ga5d9g3b9bf11872bc": ["<i>Bare your own teeth at him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "6ceec226-c28e-2375-3ee1-413f8067d048"], "h038b322dg8a3eg4045gaa65g545fb7d17a8a": ["*The rat bristles with an offended hiss.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "40a094cd-b02d-d279-1620-0d3659d138e5"], "hfdf33a95gb909g46f7ga6edg170f53832413": ["<i>Soothe him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "f50f0be8-cf99-2f21-62d0-0f567a9e7b13"], "hf9b5306bgd01ag4badg8d1bg6061ee01111e": ["*He relaxes, an appreciative squeak escaping his tiny mouth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "e962cfec-76a4-31ab-37f9-1edf97372a1b"], "h3ac0d0dfgec17g4389ga133g91213cfe1e29": ["*Hiss!*", "b61c2b37-da0d-47ad-ba9f-a4f8230f3b53", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "7c66885b-f464-3ada-9728-223df6105ee1"], "hfd0aa98eg43d1g4251ga70cg8a49c40c27ac": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Rat.html", "353efde1-8125-67dc-4322-66c75649285c"]}